I"Ù<p><a href="http://initd.org/psycopg/docs">Psycopg</a> is a trusted and reliable Python adaptor for <a href="https://www.postgresql.org">PostgreSQL</a>. It enables one to connect to a PostgreSQL database and run SQL commands, right from within Python Scripts.</p>

<p>PostgreSQL is a popular object-relational database management system ( it stores data in relations/tables with rows and columns, and tables can be linked). It is fast, reliable and open source (free).</p>
